</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:32
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='501000' id='t-501000'>So what can we do about this?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504000' id='t-504000'>There's a philosopher, Derek Parfit,</span>
