<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='510000' id='t-510000'>He said that, &quot;We might neglect our future selves</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='513000' id='t-513000'>because of some failure of belief or imagination.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517000' id='t-517000'>That is to say,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='519000' id='t-519000'>we somehow might not believe that we're going to get old,</span>
