</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:04
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='533000' id='t-533000'>So my coauthors and I have used computers,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='536000' id='t-536000'>the greatest tool of our time,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='538000' id='t-538000'>to assist people's imagination</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='540000' id='t-540000'>and help them imagine what it might be like</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='543000' id='t-543000'>to go into the future.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='545000' id='t-545000'>And I'll show you some of these tools right here.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='548000' id='t-548000'>The first is called the distribution builder.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='550000' id='t-550000'>It shows people what the future might be like</span>
