</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='581000' id='t-581000'>Now you can try to move your outcomes around.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='584000' id='t-584000'>You can try to manipulate your fate, like this person is doing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='587000' id='t-587000'>but it costs you something to do it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='589000' id='t-589000'>It means that you have to save more today.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593000' id='t-593000'>Once you find an investment that you're happy with,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='595000' id='t-595000'>what people do is they click &quot;done&quot;</span>
