11:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='655000' id='t-655000'>Now people are motivated through emotions,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='658000' id='t-658000'>but different people find different things motivating.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='661000' id='t-661000'>This is a simulation</span>
